{"tid":679892,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[推到有人唱] 臨完場 輸波都只怪膠猁乏勁 (改：天命最高)","createTime":"2018-05-26T21:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T23:59:04.000Z","uid":34701,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"593a60ba246692ef4f3826817b3e6ed4d1401ac4","tid":679892,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:51:01.000Z","msg":"臨完場 輸波都只怪膠猁乏勁&nbsp;<br />\n整定 球員醜態現形&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n誰嫌頹 敗局亦不易平定&nbsp;<br />\n遑論領先 賤蝗~&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n別高興 別以為靠高普&nbsp;<br />\n萬季千季都會依猁意願來留步&nbsp;<br />\n下一季 前四仍會不保&nbsp;<br />\n若要賭 光臨當舖&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n誰贏誰 英超不需買兵便命定&nbsp;<br />\n他年 輪迴今季劇情&nbsp;<br />\n誰亡誰 猁在歷史下效命&nbsp;<br />\n如犯錯般受刑<br />\n<br />\n別高興 別以為靠高普&nbsp;<br />\n來季今季都會依猁意願來停步&nbsp;<br />\n下一季 前四仍會不保&nbsp;<br />\n若再賭 輸埋隻撈&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n別失敬 別以為要聲討&nbsp;<br />\n上季失冠都是依猁意願來營造&nbsp;<br />\n在今季 回顧誰教得好&nbsp;<br />\n若要數 渣士最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e10b60b130d8649b5a2c594a4b27dabe1be23b2","tid":679892,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:54:45.000Z","msg":"呢首應該可以不停循環再用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f601e72f924890f235a29f6723aefffa2252bf5","tid":679892,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T21:57:44.000Z","msg":"Karius<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e23ac8fb9bfebadf3ef9d891954d2b7ec912aa","tid":679892,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T22:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6688605344946204ac3f44085afa3a25897c470d","tid":679892,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T22:16:12.000Z","msg"